text: On February 16, 2018, an earthquake with a magnitude 7.2 hit in southern Mexico. One report said that a military helicopter crashed near the earthquake. It's most likely that 14 people were killed, and that 15 people were hurt from the earthquake. ==References== Earthquakes Oaxaca Oaxaca Category:Oaxaca Oaxaca
title: 2018 Oaxaca earthquake
